breaking by 1991 in accordance with legislation passed by congress 
in 1986 it is to be located at and is designed to complete the 
memorial gate of arlington cemetery the gate was left unfinished 
during the depression 
harp said the grove of 49 trees in the georgia teams design was 
designed to symbolize a guard of sentries he said an underground 
