significant even historic document 
the declaration will satisfy the very profound desire our 
peoples have to heal the wounds of the past with understanding and 
reconciliation and to build a better future kohl said at the 
dinner 
klein said kohl urged the soviet leader to make quick 
progress at the vienna talks on reducing conventional arms 
we are not against quick progress in the vienna talks were 
for it gerasimov said at the briefing with klein we will be 
