parliament once described by a member as the 
longestrunning farce in the west end has been added to britains 
fall television schedule 
the mother of parliaments voted monday to admit television 
cameras but adopted rules ensuring the electronic eye will be too 
polite to notice rude behavior 
if someone behaves in a disorderly silly or boorish manner 
why should this be kept from the people who elected them asked 
