looking back on the ups downs and excesses of 
his 60year career as an entertainer sammy davis jr comments 
im probably the only man who was dr franenstein and the 
monster 
a 60year anniversary he started hoofing onstage at the age of 
3 is cause for retrospection and davis was in a reflective mood 
he also has a new autobiography why me farrar straus 
giroux 1895 an update of his 1965 memoir yes i can he 
talked openly about his years of excess as he sat at the bar of his 
holmby hills home uncharacteristically he was nursing a soft drink 
i created my own monster he said nobody put a gun to my 
