be deleted from the certification the department said in a legal 
opinion 
the department also said that the imposition of forced 
commercial advertising on schoolchildren may violate the state 
constitution 
educators and tv watchdogs are reacting more favorably to the 
daily cnn newsroom due to start aug 14 in time for the fall 
school term a full year before channel one would be available in 
