would be a moneymaker while discovery with its daily hourlong 
assignment discovery expects to break even by enlisting 
corporate and foundation underwriters 
the discovery underwriters will be identified onscreen but their 
names will never interrupt either of the two educational segments 
planned for each hour thus students will never have to see the 
sponsorship billboards 
the education community has reserved its highest praise for the 
discovery series which starts sept 18 for one thing it is 
divided into systematic teacherfriendly curriculum blocks social 
studies teachers for example will know that documentaries in their 
field are shown on tuesdays 
furthermore the network is getting educational rights to each 
program so teachers can tape segments at their convenience and use 
them if and when they want teachers consequently remain in control 
of what happens in their classrooms rather than being forced to 
show a daily program such as channel one that may or may not be 
the best use of time that day 
if there are ways to provide this technology when where and 
how the teacher feels it best enhances instruction discussion and 
comprehension then it is to be applauded said manya ungar 
president of the national pta if it doesnt its a detriment 
