northrop corps defense systems division here for possible 
overcharging on military contracts according to a published report 
company spokeswoman maria oharenko acknowledged the probe but 
would not reveal its focus 
we are aware of a government investigation and company 
documents were subpoenaed she said we are working with the 
government on the document request 
agents from the us attorneys office visited the defense 
systems division in this chicago suburb last week seeking documents 
related to the probe she told the daily herald in arlington heights 
the newspaper reported last weekend that the probe involves 
accusations that northrop improperly billed the government for 
defense work 
