cineplex odeon corp announced monday it will 
increase the weekend ticket price at its manhattan theaters to 
750 blaming the hike on the cost renovating its movie houses and 
high operating costs in new york 
the 50cent price increase takes effect friday after 6 pm and 
for all saturday and sunday shows at the torontobased companys 48 
screens at 23 manhattan theaters weekday prices remain the same 
cineplex bought the rko century warner theater chain in 1986 and 
noted monday that it had pledged to renovate and refurbish each 
theater in the new york area 
by the end of august the company said it will have accomplished 
that goal at 75 percent of its manhattan screens 
cineplex broke the 6 ticket price barrier in manhattan when it 
raised it price to 7 in late 1987 the move prompted protests 
outside its theaters that drew mayor edward i koch among others 
cineplex is one of the largest film exhibitors in north america 
with 1820 screens in 500 locations 
